column2: Light Elemental Sword Tech.  Deals damage based on both ATK and MAG.
Dark Elemental Sword Tech.  Based on the Devil's Number.
Spear Tech.  Deals damage based on how slow you are compared to your enemy.
Physical Sword Tech.  Deals damage to all enemies in a circle.
Dark Dagger Tech.  Weak attack that also poisons the enemy.
Water Magic Tech.  Fires a single shot of water at range.
Healing Magic Tech.  Heals at least 25 HP.
Fire Magic Tech.  Fires a single shot of fire at range.
Fire Magic Tech.  Fires a single shot of fire at range.
